reviewText: Really good learning material for the GPSMAP62 beginner. I learned ALOT about using my GPS with this program.
I had thought it was a book. The CD was really bad & I wouldn't want anyone to spend money on this. See UTube it has more on the Device.

This book offers good basic guidance that will get the novice started down the right path.  I learned about some functions of my GPSMap 62st that I probably would never have used had I not read this guide.
I purchased this DVD to better understand my Garmin Gps and it surpassed my expectations.  If you want to totally understand your Garmin Maps GPS this is the key to all the mystery.

This video did not instruct me in way to use the GPS. It told me what buttons did what but not how to use them. On line I could find out what all the buttons did. I wanted to know how to make a trek and so on. This video would get a very minimal rating. I would not recommend this video to any body else.
This was a disappointing purchase. It was not very helpful. Need to have better ways to illustrate how to use the GPS.
